00:17:19,990 --> 00:17:25,390
Is it a good idea to display luxury brands and other signals of status 

251
00:17:25,670 --> 00:17:27,790
It depends on the situation 

252
00:17:28,400 --> 00:17:31,860
Studies have shown that people who appear to be wealthy

253
00:17:31,860 --> 00:17:34,550
Tend to be considered more intelligent 

254
00:17:34,550 --> 00:17:38,190
Disciplined , and competent than those who do not 

255
00:17:38,670 --> 00:17:44,430
But new research found that people believe someone who shows off their social status

256
00:17:44,470 --> 00:17:48,470
Cares more about benefiting themselves than helping others 

257
00:17:49,070 --> 00:17:52,830
This means people are less willing to collaborate with them 

258
00:17:53,500 --> 00:17:57,380
Modesty may be key when cooperation is essential 

259
00:17:57,530 --> 00:18:03,650
But the researchers also found that in some cases , status signaling has advantages 

260
00:18:04,200 --> 00:18:08,660
Experiments showed that participants were less likely to choose someone

261
00:18:08,660 --> 00:18:13,850
Who signals their wealth or status to join a group seeking cooperative members 

262
00:18:14,300 --> 00:18:17,580
But participants were more likely to choose that person

263
00:18:17,700 --> 00:18:20,660
When they were looking for a competitive team member 

264
00:18:21,230 --> 00:18:25,710
These findings suggest that people should change how they present themselves

265
00:18:25,710 --> 00:18:27,870
Depending on their social goal 

266
00:18:28,340 --> 00:18:30,660
This is the era of social media 

267
00:18:30,740 --> 00:18:35,180
People can easily share their wealth and status to large audiences 

268
00:18:35,530 --> 00:18:38,210
But they need to consider the consequences 

269
00:18:38,990 --> 00:18:43,230
Posting about luxury purchases and expensive vacations online

270
00:18:43,390 --> 00:18:47,190
May help you to persuade others and frighten competitors 

271
00:18:47,730 --> 00:18:52,370
But it could also signal to potential friends or future employers

272
00:18:52,530 --> 00:18:55,970
